text: Võ Ngọc Toàn (born 20 October 1994) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a midfielder for V-League (Vietnam) club SHB Đà Nẵng. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:V.League 1 players Category:Song Lam Nghe An F.C. players
